# Changelog edits (`context/changelog/`)

- Follow patterns in **`context/changelog/changelog-template.md`**.
- **Per-app** files: `changelog-bss-b2b-lock-login-password.md`, `changelog-bss-b2b-request-a-quote-quick.md`, `changelog-bss-b2b-wholesale-solution.md`; package rollups: `changelog-package-*.md`.
- Preserve **duplicate version labels** when the source had them; do not invent new version numbers to “fix” duplicates.
- Wording should stay **merchant-facing** and consistent with how each app names features in **`context/*_APP_CONTEXT.md`**.
